Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:15.22,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}微风拍打着寂寞的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:23.41,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}你的身旁 铃声回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:31.61,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}时光重叠 寂寞渐渐飞散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:39.32,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}向着天空许愿 许下这永远的誓言　My Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:45.07,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}被倾盆大雨所打湿的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:48.08,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}just believeＸbelieveＸbelieve
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:56.33,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}再小的声音我也会赶到你身旁 仅此而已
